name: Time Tracking
query:
select
    obj1.name  as "Sales Order:Link/Sales Order:140",
    obj1.date_and_time  as "Order Time & Date:Datetime:160",
    obj1.estimated_delivery_time  as "Estimated Delivery Time:Int:140",
    obj2.name  as "Delivery Note:Link/Delivery Note:140",
    obj2.date_and_time as "Delivery Date & Time:Datetime:160",
    obj2.estimated_invoice_time as "Estimated Invoice Time:Int:160",
    TIMEDIFF(obj2.date_and_time,obj1.date_and_time)  as "Time Taken For Delivery::140",
    TIMEDIFF(obj4.date_and_time,obj2.date_and_time)  as "Time Taken For Invoice::140"
    from `tabSales Order` obj1, `tabDelivery Note` obj2, `tabDelivery Note Item` obj3, `tabSales Invoice` obj4, `tabSales Invoice Item` obj5
    where obj3.parent = obj2.name and obj5.parent = obj4.name
    and obj1.name = obj3.against_sales_order and obj2.name = obj5.delivery_note;
